quran[10{c,v,t}:
23,18,aur hum hi ne aasman se aik andazay ke sath pani nazilkiya. phir is ko zameen mein thehra diya aur hum is ke nabood kardainay par bhi Qadir hain
23,19,"phir hum ne is se tumahray liye khajoron aur angarro ke baagh banaye, un mein tumahray liye bohat se meway peda hotay hain. aur un mein se tum khatay bhi ho"
23,20,aur woh darakht bhi ( hum hi ne pedakiya ) jo tor seena mein peda hota hai ( yani Zaitoon ka darakht ke ) khanay ke liye roghan aur saalan liye hue aُgta hai
23,21,aur tumahray liye charpayon mein bhi Ibrat ( aur nishani ) hai ke un ke piton mein hai is se hum tumhe ( doodh ) pilate hain aur tumahray liye un mein aur bhi bohat se faiday hain aur baaz ko tum khatay bhi ho
23,22,aur un par aur kashtiyon par tum sawaar hotay ho
23,23,"aur hum ne Nooh ko un ki qoum ki taraf bheja to unhon ne un se kaha ke ae qoum! khuda hi ki ibadat karo is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi,kiya tum drtay nahi"
23,24,to un ki qoum ke sardar jo kafir they kehnay lagey ke yeh to tum hi jaissa aadmi hai. tum par barayi haasil karni chahta hai. aur agar khuda chahta to farishtay utaar deta. hum ne apne aglay baap dada mein to yeh baat kabhi suni nahi thi
23,25,is aadmi ko to deewangi ( ka aarzah ) hai to is ke baray mein kuch muddat intzaar karo
23,26,Nooh ne kaha ke perwar-digaar unhon ne mujhe jhtlaya hai to meri madad kar
23,27,"pas hum ne un ki taraf wahi bhaije ke hamaray samnay aur hamaray hukum se aik kashti banaao. phir jab hamara hukum aa puhanche aur tanoor ( pani se bhar kar ) josh maarny lagey to sab ( qisam ke hewanat ) mein jora jora ( yani nar aur madah ) do do kashti mein bitha do aur apne ghar walon ko bhi, so un ke jin ki nisbat un mein se ( halaak honay ka ) hukum pehlay sadir hochuka hai. aur zaalmon ke baray mein hum se kuch nah kehna, woh zaroor duubo diye jayen ge"
